Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.77,0:00:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll become a different Banri and start over.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.03,0:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.99,0:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to you, I feel like I've suddenly become free.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me do something to thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I see your friend at the hospital, I'll give him a message.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.72,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A message?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.39,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you shouldn't come here alone anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your signal will reach him eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make sure it does.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My signal...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too late for my signal to reach him.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.08,0:01:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing I can do anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only way I can think is that
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.92,0:01:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if I'd made it in time, \Nthat wouldn't have happened to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'd made it in time...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would've held his hand tight
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and never let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going now.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, what's your message?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell him, "You can do it."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not supposed to say that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.51,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again? Why do I keep having that dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.14,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}did Linda say to me then?
