Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time came for our first event of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the Awa dance festival \Nthe Festival Club is participating in.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.30,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Other universities and Awa dance\N preservation societies are here as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they look like girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are girls in our club!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot. Fan...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you guys can hang around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.58,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The building's air conditioned, and it feels great inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.00,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We let you use that space so you could change.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We match.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm a beautiful woman dressed as a man.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so handsome!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so handsome today.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, you really do look better than me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell I'm not used to these clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's a battle of charm.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your girlfriend's having a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hunk of junk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a modern-day Yaoya Oshichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a job for her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it heat stroke?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She had lots of energy until a minute ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.04,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just n-nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom again!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's walking funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already been to the\N bathroom about thirty times.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it, that's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bladder's empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. Calm down and think carefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your urge to pee...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My urge to pee...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a phantom urge.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a phantom urge!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to calm down, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.22,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's even more of a hunk of junk than I imagined.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's out of oil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put on your lipstick, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, RoboGirl!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No help for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, RoboGirl.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget how funny you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Adieu, RoboGirl-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd leave one of our own behind?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.15,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosshi-senpai, hasn't the time come to teach the first years about {\i1}that{\i0\fscx20} {\r}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"That," huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do {\i1}that{\i0\fscx20} {\r}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our only hope.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.34,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.34,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahoy, ahoy, ahoy, ahoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.28,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, ahoy, ahoy, ahoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.88,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,RoboGirl!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.56,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to our first festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dismissed for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fireworks show later at the riverbank near here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to attend.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing's too much trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's at least change into sneakers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet will be at camp.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai was wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You danced well too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a ghost again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.78,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feelings for Linda still remain in Banri's heart,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until now, I've thought of him as my younger twin.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if he didn't notice me,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.84,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he respected the\N feelings I'd always nurtured.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he abandoned me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kouko, have you been to a fireworks show before?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though he still has feelings for Linda,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The booming explosions are amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's forced himself to pretend there's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.65,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He rejected the feelings I had to leave behind in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll curse you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll become an evil spirit and make you unhappy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It suddenly started raining!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We've gotta hurry up and find shelter!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.06,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The seminar house we got for our camp is closed for repairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in September.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been like this since summer vacation started.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The fireworks display was canceled,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed the film showing,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yana-san suddenly canceled our plans to hang out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.84,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, it's so hot every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, my lover.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You were, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.47,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm a surprising woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the stairs?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sprinted up them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could surprise you as you came to meet me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You were surprised, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the spice...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of love!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, I ended up like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you a curried yakisoba that's so delicious,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll blow your pain away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakisoba?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought ingredients,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm ready to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously great!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks fantastic on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you wear that whenever you cook at home!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so feminine!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a surprising girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it! Love it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you with whatever!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to help me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl thing, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, just sit.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might need this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I brought it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to wear this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, put your hands here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take them out, it's game over.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Banri, do you know about that man?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What man?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In a snowy village,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.14,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a middle-aged man living an ecological, healthy,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and sustainable life with his mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.52,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that man is having sexual relations with a bird.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the important part.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.24,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is the sad truth that the man is a peeping Tom.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.08,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The bird is chirping suspiciously— chirp, chirp, chirp—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and acting strangely behind the door.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The man can't contain his curiosity, and in the end, he commits the crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,his strange but happy life with the bird comes to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the crane wife?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, um, it means...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't watch you while you cook?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a terrible storyteller.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you'll make me really nervous if you watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So stay right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Face the other way and don't move.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my very best.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My curried yakisoba will be delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Banri, did you hear that our trip was canceled?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.85,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could reminisce about the time we got lost in those mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that was such a great memory.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.57,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, camp or no camp, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to wash some vegetables.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.03,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to cut some vegetables and meat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to sauté some vegetables and meat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to add the noodles.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.90,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll season them and quickly finish them off like I always do.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kouko?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll burn.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.97,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what you think it is, Banri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A joke!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A joke?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my best joke!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Air yakisoba!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Air yakisoba?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Laugh, Banri!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Try laughing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the spice...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of love too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I really meant to make it myself, at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But while practicing at home,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I started getting nervous, \Nand I couldn't even hold a knife properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so weak under pressure.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.35,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So then our maid saw me and started making it herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "You're useless! Give me that."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed she called her\N employer's daughter "useless."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a foul mouth, but she's really nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She even lent me this apron.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.83,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we talk a little more?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll attend a proper cooking school.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal's not good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.01,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make you think, "She's awesome! Her feminine charm is through the roof!"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer vacation,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.10,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll throw myself into the culinary tiger's den and train.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Culinary tiger's den?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll do that...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and cancel my family vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Barcelona, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A long vacation sounds nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Banri, you'll...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you spent it with me, you'd have a boring summer just killing time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could be together the whole time too, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Banri, you're forgetting something.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't go to Barcelona. Stay with me."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell her to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.97,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't complain if she abandons you eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.68,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday a better man will appear, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Banri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.06,0:21:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Find someone who can make you delicious curried yakisoba.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make you even unhappier.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that voice?
